          <h5>Rules</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Teams must create drafts based on a colour, and all their hero picks must match that colour</li>
            <li>The first phase of banning is normal</li>
            <li>Teams do not commit to their colour until their first pick</li>
            <li>After a team’s first pick they must say what colour they are in all chat</li>
            <li>The rest of the draft is normal, except teams must only pick heroes of their chosen colour</li>
