          <h3 class="card-title mt-2 text-center">Letter Draft</h3>
          <hr>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h5>Number of Players</h5>
              <p>5v5</p>
              <h5>Game Mode</h5>
              <p>Captains Mode</p>
              <h5>Rules</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Teams must create their draft from heroes starting with the same letter</li>
                <li>Teams pick two different letters to pick their heroes from</li>
                <li>Letter picking will be determined by a mini-draft with “letter bans” and “letter picks”</li>
                <li>Team will have 30 sec to pick or ban each letter (No reserve time)</li>
                <li>A letter can only be picked or banned once</li>
                <li>The draft will take place in Discord, and pick order will be determined by a coin toss</li>
                <li>After the Letters have been chosen the Captains Mode draft will be used to pick heroes</li>
                <li>The previous coin toss will be used to determine pick order</li>
                <li>There will be no bans. Instead teams will ban heroes that start with letters not picked by a team. (Example: If team 1 has letters A and C, and team 2 has M and W then teams will ban heroes that DON’T start with A,C,M, or W)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h5>Letter Draft Order</h5>
              <table class="table table-striped">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Team 1</th>
                    <th>Team 2</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr><td>Letter <b>ban</b></td><td>Wait</td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Wait</td><td>Letter <b>ban</b></td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Letter <b>ban</b></td><td>Wait</td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Wait</td><td>Letter <b>ban</b></td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Letter <b>pick</b></td><td>Wait</td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Wait</td><td>Letter <b>pick</b></td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Wait</td><td>Letter <b>pick</b></td></tr>
                  <tr><td>Letter <b>pick</b></td><td>Wait</td></tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
