          <h5>Number of Players</h5>
          <p>5v5 (Minimum 1 person watching)</p>
          <h5>Game Mode</h5>
          <p>Captains Mode</p>
          <h5>Rules</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Teams will have the drafts decided by players who are watching the game</li>
            <li>Audience members will take turns picking and banning heroes in a rotation</li>
            <li>Audience members may pick or ban for either team</li>
            <li>All Chat is permitted for the audience (no harmful language or flaming)</li>
            <li>Players be aware that the audience may all chat gg, so do not stop playing if that does happen</li>

          </ul>
